snippet.title: trailer
snippet.description:
Deteriation Game which is a misspelling of deterioration,
is a game about exploring your dreams and figuring out who you are.
Travel through surreal recreations of your memory, or is it all just real?

https://stenblood.itch.io/deteriation-game

- 0 / 5 Endings implemented.
- Currently around 20 worlds all based off things that happened to you.
- A dread that always follows you around.
MADE FOR DREAM DIARY JAM 6.
